2. Platform Overview
Nervus is a digital platform that encourages users to participate in daily missions to spread kindness through captured moments. Gemini Justice verifies the authenticity of user submissions to maintain the integrity of the platform. Nervus also offers in-app purchases, including digital coins, and features such as leaderboards, competitions, and community challenges.

3. User Responsibilities
Account Creation: To use Nervus, you must create an account. You are responsible for keeping your login credentials secure and are liable for any activity that occurs under your account.
Authenticity: All content, including captured moments and messages, must be genuine. Misrepresentation, manipulation, or any form of deceit will lead to suspension or termination of your account.
Respect for the Community: Users must engage respectfully. Any form of harassment, abusive language, or harmful behavior will result in removal or banning from the platform.
4. Gemini Verification
By using Nervus, you agree to allow Gemini Justice to verify your content submissions. Gemini moderates and validates user content to ensure authenticity and fairness in all aspects of the platform, including leaderboards and challenges. The decisions made by Gemini are final and cannot be contested.

5. Leaderboard and Competitions
Nervus hosts various challenges and competitions:

Leaderboard: Points are awarded for acts of kindness, and the top participants are showcased monthly. Prizes are awarded to the top three participants each month.
People’s Choice Challenges: Users can participate in challenges judged by the community and Gemini. Decisions by Gemini in these challenges are final.
6. In-App Purchases and Virtual Currency (Coins)
Nervus includes the option to purchase virtual currency (“Coins”) through in-app purchases. Coins are used to participate in certain activities or challenges. Coins are not redeemable for cash and have no monetary value outside of Nervus. Once purchased, Coins cannot be refunded or transferred to other users. All transactions are final.

Withdrawals of Gems
Users can accumulate "Gems" on the platform, which may be withdrawn by sending an email request to Nervus support at contactnervus@gmail.com. Nervus reserves the right to verify the validity of withdrawal requests and process them within a reasonable time frame. Any fraudulent, duplicate, or spammy requests will result in the suspension of withdrawal privileges and possible account termination.

7. Monetary Transactions and Fraud Prevention
